rown, Frog Crown, Kobold Jester's Crown and even my cute little STR booster, Grandmaster's Headband. But I'd jump all over this in a heartbeat. But real priority, Ebony Headband!&nbsp;&nbsp;/drool  On with the show and good day.<br>&nbsp;<br>Antiochus Oogly<br>55 Master (and growing!)<br>Mithaniel Marr</td></tr>
